Seun Kuti took to Instagram to celebrate his daughter who turns 7 today.

The singer shared a photo he took with his daughter Adara Anikulapo Kuti and expressed how much she means to him.

He wrote: “Happy 7th birthday Adara Anikulapo Kuti!

“Since I met you, you have brought me plenty of joy and understanding. You have made me brave, given me focus and the drive to embrace my calling.

“I am happy to have you in my life, like a compass and also my validation. You make me proud little empress. Welcome to the age of 7.”

